{"tid":1639214,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"絲打入一入嚟！夜防狗公必備之選！","createTime":"2019-10-08T14:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T00:55:29.000Z","uid":308751,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8244954f6e1f4920b2a6a8543aba21ef59c85444","tid":1639214,"uid":308751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:25:02.000Z","msg":"最近夜晚唔係好安全<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">尤其係嗰啲夜晚自己一個人行，又索又正嘅絲打</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n好心你地唔好日日帶住枝<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香水</strong></span>出街啦，啲女神香氣想引死啲狗公咩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小妹自問唔靚，冇狗公埋身，但就好惹蚊！<br />\n所以日日都袋住枝<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">蚊拍水</span>出街街～<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q9mAboh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ9mAboh.jpg&h=9babf30b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢枝就好似幾work咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫時係我搵到DEET濃度高啲嘅一枝<br />\n但係就未試過，唔知佢噴霧效果如何<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WfqM2wn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWfqM2wn.jpg&h=26f807e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人試過呢枝就麻麻地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢太過油，所以做唔到噴霧效果<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0fEmRro.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0fEmRro.png&h=741ce91f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其他巴絲有推介都分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能有氣質絲打覺得大枝唔方便帶出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個時候咪入落啲樽仔度用囉<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">不過萬一俾狗公捉住，就唔知會唔會比佢哋老屈係其他液體</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma